### RescueGuide API - Location Controller Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5238/api/location

### Get all locations
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get location by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Get location by ID (non-existent)
GET {{baseUrl}}/999

### Create new location
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 6,
  "latitude": 48.2082,
  "longitude": 16.3738
}

### Create another location
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 7,
  "latitude": 48.3069,
  "longitude": 14.2858
}

### Update location
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "latitude": 48.2500,
  "longitude": 16.3800
}

### Delete location
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1

### Delete non-existent location
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/999

### Update non-existent location
PUT {{baseUrl}}/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 999,
  "latitude": 50.0,
  "longitude": 15.0
}

